{
 "name": "RPlog_Simulated_Evacuation",
 "title": "Simulated Evacuation",
 "summary": "The Caspian Democratic Union stages a fleet wargame over Charros IV: a simulated mass-casualty evacuation defended by green Caspian flight crews against an attacking force secretly commanded by Marshal Axel Vichten and the gunship captain Lynae Cassius. While news anchors Allie Vraill and her co-host narrate the exercise and dignitaries -- Crestian Tarasar, his daughter Atsvara, Ssanyu, Salin Fawzy, and the spymaster Malif -- watch from the observation deck, the technician Selko Aronat and the model Lady Sha-Cha Cha wrestle a malfunctioning camera droid and the flustered presenter Nara struggles into a flight suit. Vichten's tiny force of skiprays and the modified Z-95 Chimaera screen the gunships and savage the evacuation transports before the defenders' Vulture droids and squadrons finally overwhelm and 'kill' the attackers. Though officially destroyed, Vichten and Cassius use the mock battle to school the young crews in tactics, and Crestian closes the games with thanks to the participating designers and commanders.",
